patthana23.10:1.1_0: Nakusalaṁ nasekkhaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā kusalo sekkho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.10:1.1_1: (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha …pe… āsevane tīṇi …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
patthana23.10:2.1_0: Nakusalaṁ naasekkhaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā abyākato asekkho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.10:3.1_0: Nakusalaṁ nanevasekkhanāsekkhaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca abyākato nevasekkhanāsekkho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā pañca,
patthana23.10:3.1_1: adhipatiyā pañca …pe… vipāke tīṇi …pe… avigate pañca.
